""" Mail mappings (for MH)

""" repl mappings
" Attempts to undo quoting done by replies
map <Leader>> 1G:/^---/+1,$g/^[ ]*[^> ]/-1j:%g/^---/+1,$s/^[ ]*>[ ]\(>[ ]\)*//g<CR>
" Opens the file replied to (Can't rely on MH's @ link because we will
